ated GaV4S8, this relaxation dynamics that most likely mirrors coupled\norbital and polar fluctuations does not seem to be related to the dynamic\nprocesses detected in the THz regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 May 2017 15:40:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-25"}
